NAME
 version - get the version of the library

LIBRARY
  codata (-libcodata, -lcodata)

SYNOPSIS
  version()

DESCRIPTION
  Get the library version.

RETURN VALUE
  character(len=:), pointer :: fptr  Pointer to the version as string.

EXAMPLE
  Minimal example:

      use codata
      print *, "version = ", version()

SEE ALSO
  codata(3)
